name: intgr-crm-nx.yml
configuration:
spring:
  application:
    name: nttm-intgr-crm-nx
  jpa:
    database: postgresql
    hibernate:
      ddl-auto: none
    database-platform: org.hibernate.dialect.PostgreSQL95Dialect
    properties:
      hibernate:
        connection:
          release_mode: after_transaction
        temp:
          use_jdbc_metadata_defaults: false
  jmx:
    enabled: false
  rabbitmq:
    host: rabbitmq-6260
    username: admin
    password: admin
    crm_nx_notifications_queue: crm_nx_notifications
    logger_queue: logger
server:
  port: 8285
management:
  endpoints:
    web:
      path-mapping:
        prometheus: metrics
      base-path: /
      exposure:
        include: prometheus
  health.solr.enabled: false
logging:
  config: classpath:log4j2-dev.yaml
  level:
    org.hibernate: error
    org.hibernate.SQL: error
    org.zalando.logbook: trace
logbook:
  format:
    style: http
  exclude:
    - "**/metrics"
technograd:
  url: "http://ssidr004steda1.si.rt.ru/DatumNode/DatumNode.svc?wsdl&entity=oss_api.rt.TSWebService"
nx:
  url: "http://ssolb-bt1.pbs.sibir.rt.ru:47400/soap/rt/crm/ws/TSNotification?wsdl"
  user: "NTTM"
  pass: "NTTM1"
crm-nx:
  order-item-specifications: cfs_vsc_user_profile, cfs_vsc_profile, cfs_vats_user_profile, cfs_vats_telephone_profile, cfs_8800_user_profile, cfs_8800_telephone_profile, cfs_managed_wifi
nttm:
  prefix: "http://10.28.97.89:8080"
  auth:
    username: "crm_nx_intgr"
    password: "c4d123f2cb08ff2204ce80e12f884ccf"
